WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 3]

01:16.110 --> 01:17.340
If I kill her now,

01:17.910 --> 01:19.530
the fox spirit may reveal itself to save her.

01:20.750 --> 01:23.650
Now's the chance to shatter her meridians.

01:52.550 --> 01:53.810
We've been moved somewhere else?

01:58.670 --> 02:00.090
So we passed the first trial?

02:11.270 --> 02:12.250
Xiaobangchui?

02:13.870 --> 02:14.900
Xiaobangchui!

02:17.430 --> 02:18.370
You guys made it too?

02:18.670 --> 02:19.500
Xiaobangchui!

02:23.150 --> 02:24.410
You guys made it too. That's great!

02:24.430 --> 02:25.220
You're here too.

02:30.550 --> 02:32.740
Xiaobangchui, what happened to your clothes...?

02:33.320 --> 02:34.130
Don't even ask.

02:34.590 --> 02:35.900
It was all icicles and snow blades

02:35.900 --> 02:36.900
along the way.

02:36.900 --> 02:38.220
I'm lucky I didn't get skewered.

02:40.430 --> 02:43.300
Xiuyuan, how are you? Are you hurt?

02:44.990 --> 02:46.220
And it was freezing cold.

02:46.390 --> 02:47.850
I almost didn't make it.

02:50.710 --> 02:51.410
What about you guys?

02:51.800 --> 02:53.220
We ran into some kind of mystical formation.

02:54.960 --> 02:55.970
But with Ye here,

02:56.390 --> 02:57.370
nothing could stop us.

02:59.480 --> 03:01.570
So we've passed the first trial?

03:03.900 --> 03:04.530
Next...

03:05.590 --> 03:07.500
Help! Don't kill me!

03:12.990 --> 03:13.460
You...

03:21.710 --> 03:22.340
Stay back!

03:23.390 --> 03:24.370
Don't kill me!

03:42.960 --> 03:45.940
Tongzhou, is this forest the second trial?

03:48.270 --> 03:49.250
Don't touch anything.

03:50.990 --> 03:52.570
Your Highness, you really are brilliant!

04:34.470 --> 04:35.370
Stop messing around.

04:35.880 --> 04:37.500
Who knows when the second trial will end.

04:57.640 --> 04:58.450
It's miasma.

05:02.710 --> 05:04.010
- What's going on? - What's going on?

05:04.030 --> 05:05.570
- What's happening? - Are you okay?

05:19.100 --> 05:19.740
- Changyue! - Changyue!

05:28.910 --> 05:29.420
Changyue!

05:29.460 --> 05:31.500
Don't go out there! Stay in the light.

05:35.470 --> 05:36.210
- Changyue, are you okay?
- Are you okay?

05:36.230 --> 05:36.810
I'm fine.

05:49.790 --> 05:50.620
Tongzhou, what is that?

05:51.140 --> 05:51.660
This is bad.

05:54.710 --> 05:55.100
Run!

05:55.340 --> 05:57.060
Where did these wraith birds come from?

05:57.790 --> 05:59.060
They weren't part of the formation.

05:59.580 --> 06:00.420
I was careless.

06:01.340 --> 06:03.570
Didn't expect so many wraiths here.

06:04.790 --> 06:07.570
They must have been disturbed by our formation.

06:36.710 --> 06:37.210
Go!

06:52.030 --> 06:53.450
You little brat.

06:53.560 --> 06:54.980
Can't you just run away quietly? Are you crazy?

06:55.120 --> 06:55.770
I'll beat...

07:37.030 --> 07:37.660
Run!

07:39.390 --> 07:40.130
Xiaobangchui!

07:41.350 --> 07:42.180
Lei Xiuyuan!

07:47.440 --> 07:48.690
Why didn't you tell me they were gone?

07:49.790 --> 07:51.620
We were running for our lives just now.

07:51.640 --> 07:52.810
Couldn't care less about anything else.

07:56.030 --> 07:58.860
Tongzhou, this is just a trial.

07:58.960 --> 08:00.540
They can't be in real danger.

08:00.640 --> 08:02.130
Your Highness, Lei Xiuyuan

08:02.150 --> 08:03.330
isn't one of us.

08:03.680 --> 08:05.860
He's skilled. Maybe he's already escaped.

08:06.640 --> 08:07.330
Right, Tongzhou.

08:07.760 --> 08:09.180
Let's get out of this creepy forest first.

08:09.440 --> 08:10.250
It's so scary here.

08:11.640 --> 08:12.420
Tongzhou,

08:12.760 --> 08:14.420
please, let's go first, okay?

08:19.520 --> 08:20.010
Let's go.

08:27.320 --> 08:27.770
Let's go!

08:32.790 --> 08:33.250
Get in!

08:33.320 --> 08:34.330
No, no!

08:34.910 --> 08:36.260
Caves are full of monsters and ghosts.

08:36.590 --> 08:37.090
I'm not going.

09:04.040 --> 09:05.610
This cave seems really deep.

09:13.350 --> 09:14.970
Hope there isn't anything evil in here.

09:22.200 --> 09:22.850
Wind?

09:23.280 --> 09:24.610
So there's an exit here?

09:26.830 --> 09:28.060
We need to get out fast.

09:29.200 --> 09:31.020
I don't want to be chased by those crazy birds again.

09:37.470 --> 09:38.060
Um...

09:40.400 --> 09:41.260
you go in first.

10:01.160 --> 10:01.970
What's going on?

10:04.830 --> 10:05.210
Let's go.

10:07.980 --> 10:08.730
It's a dead end!

10:09.590 --> 10:11.060
Why are these creepy things everywhere?

10:11.420 --> 10:13.060
Ghost butterflies of the deep valley, feeding on spirits and bones.

10:13.350 --> 10:14.060
They're bone-devouring butterflies.

10:14.300 --> 10:15.420
What a cursed name.

10:15.750 --> 10:16.810
Is this also part of the trial?

10:26.980 --> 10:27.810
Block them!

10:30.940 --> 10:31.690
Hang in there.

10:31.980 --> 10:33.420
You have plenty of spirit power. You can do this!

10:36.300 --> 10:37.300
Hang in there.

10:37.510 --> 10:38.140
Hold on.

10:39.680 --> 10:40.780
Shall I transfer spirit power to you?

10:55.340 --> 10:55.940
Stop!

10:57.870 --> 11:00.540
I'm sorry, really.

11:02.230 --> 11:04.260
I can't die yet. I still have to save Master...

11:05.510 --> 11:06.210
Master?

11:06.870 --> 11:09.420
This is a life-saving talisman I made

11:09.630 --> 11:10.900
using a century of my cultivation.

11:11.340 --> 11:13.780
Remember, it only works once.

11:14.750 --> 11:17.020
Only use it when you absolutely have to.

11:19.940 --> 11:21.730
Master, don't fail me now.

11:42.980 --> 11:43.420
Here.

11:49.220 --> 11:49.780
Are you okay?

11:56.990 --> 11:58.810
Is the talisman going to destroy him too?

12:00.180 --> 12:01.330
Wait, you...

12:01.710 --> 12:02.810
What did you put inside me?

12:03.100 --> 12:04.140
You can't die.

12:04.300 --> 12:05.140
Wait, hey!

12:05.470 --> 12:07.300
If you die, I can't answer to His Highness.

12:09.060 --> 12:09.690
What's wrong?

12:18.940 --> 12:19.940
My Lord.

12:30.750 --> 12:31.420
Tongzhou!

12:32.590 --> 12:33.210
Tongzhou?

12:34.660 --> 12:35.850
Once Zhao Mingli finishes scouting,

12:36.110 --> 12:37.140
you go back to the capital with him.

12:38.110 --> 12:39.490
Tongzhou!

12:40.040 --> 12:42.660
Tongzhou, I swear

12:42.870 --> 12:44.730
I didn't mean to hurt Xiaobangchui.

12:44.990 --> 12:45.810
Really.

12:46.830 --> 12:49.140
Having the intent to harm is no different from doing it.

12:53.440 --> 12:53.970
Tongzhou.

13:42.320 --> 13:42.850
Tongzhou.

13:53.870 --> 13:54.450
Are you okay?

14:19.590 --> 14:20.260
Be careful.

14:21.400 --> 14:22.140
Here, sit down.

14:25.230 --> 14:26.260
This isn't a trial.

14:26.990 --> 14:28.300
This is murder!

14:32.320 --> 14:35.690
No, the academy wouldn't kill anyone in the trial.

14:36.350 --> 14:37.420
We're almost dying.

14:37.830 --> 14:39.420
Why haven't the masters shown up?

14:46.510 --> 14:48.540
What was your deal at the cave entrance last night?

14:48.560 --> 14:49.540
What formation were you setting up?

15:29.800 --> 15:30.660
What are you thinking about?

15:48.440 --> 15:49.260
Answer me.

15:53.710 --> 15:54.300
Don't go.

15:55.920 --> 15:56.660
Don't leave me.

15:58.800 --> 15:59.540
Let go!

16:01.800 --> 16:03.210
You almost got me killed again!

16:04.080 --> 16:05.260
I've got you figured out.

16:05.590 --> 16:07.140
You never change!

16:07.830 --> 16:09.060
I knew it the moment I saw you.

16:15.110 --> 16:18.490
Master once said those with abundant spirit power command natural authority,

16:18.750 --> 16:19.660
and all spirits avoid them.

16:20.920 --> 16:22.780
Could Master's talisman

16:22.870 --> 16:24.330
have boosted his cultivation,

16:24.750 --> 16:25.900
spiking his power

16:26.470 --> 16:28.490
and turning him from a jinx into a bodyguard?

16:30.750 --> 16:31.570
What did you know?

16:33.350 --> 16:34.330
I knew

16:34.750 --> 16:36.940
you were naturally gifted, lean, and tall.

16:36.960 --> 16:38.690
From now on, I'll...

16:39.160 --> 16:41.020
You'll stick with me. I'll protect you.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.690
Her magic is clearly weak,

16:47.320 --> 16:48.730
yet I keep failing to get her.

16:49.160 --> 16:50.300
I'll have to make a risky move.

16:50.960 --> 16:53.180
You're not saying anything, so that means you agree.

16:55.350 --> 16:56.210
It's settled then!

17:03.400 --> 17:04.090
Not again.

17:23.920 --> 17:24.530
Tongzhou.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.860
Riyan? When did it come out?

17:38.640 --> 17:40.450
No. It's not the real one.

17:42.880 --> 17:44.820
So this is the Nine-Tailed Fox Zhenyunzi was looking for?

17:49.960 --> 17:51.660
Your Highness, you're a genius.

17:51.920 --> 17:53.450
This fox spirit is no match for you.

17:54.510 --> 17:56.860
We'll head off first so we don't get in your way.

17:57.990 --> 17:59.450
- It's part of the trial too. - Let go.

18:00.160 --> 18:00.940
Let's fight it together.

18:01.230 --> 18:02.940
Go die yourself if you want. Don't drag me into it.

18:25.990 --> 18:27.340
Your Highness, look,

18:27.470 --> 18:28.770
I really can't bear to leave you.

18:29.070 --> 18:30.420
I'll back you up. Let's beat it together.

18:31.550 --> 18:33.180
Its power is in its tail. Cut off its tail!

19:07.790 --> 19:08.900
This fox spirit has a strange aura.

19:08.990 --> 19:10.490
Doesn't seem like a thousand-year-old spirit.

19:28.070 --> 19:30.010
One test and we'll know if it's real.

19:35.710 --> 19:36.380
Tongzhou!

19:37.400 --> 19:38.140
Xiaobangchui!

19:39.790 --> 19:41.730
Wait, wait... hold on.

19:45.790 --> 19:49.050
Do you know Riyan?

19:53.440 --> 19:55.010
He's my friend. Also a big white fox.

19:56.360 --> 19:57.450
Wait,

19:58.550 --> 19:59.490
let me finish.

19:59.790 --> 20:00.450
Let me finish.

20:20.340 --> 20:21.860
You scumbag! You used me as bait?

20:33.440 --> 20:34.340
- Xiaobangchui! - Xiuyuan!

21:00.160 --> 21:03.580
Strange. I've seen a belly full of grass,

21:04.400 --> 21:06.010
but never a belly full of fur.

21:06.990 --> 21:07.770
Its evil spiritual energy isn't strong.

21:09.200 --> 21:10.010
Could it be a clone?

21:16.030 --> 21:18.100
Where is the exit?

21:21.710 --> 21:23.820
Hey, wake up.

21:25.230 --> 21:26.970
Are these all your shed hairs?

21:29.470 --> 21:30.420
Are you balding?

21:31.070 --> 21:31.940
You're the one balding!

21:32.400 --> 21:34.720
I've been eating Lingzhi and Caowu for years.

21:34.720 --> 21:35.620
My fur is thick and shiny.

21:36.100 --> 21:37.580
I've only shed a single strand in all these years.

21:39.790 --> 21:40.940
So only one strand.

21:42.200 --> 21:43.660
Which one is the real one?

22:10.990 --> 22:11.900
Found it.

22:29.920 --> 22:31.140
Fox spirit, reveal yourself!

22:37.790 --> 22:40.380
Who would've thought? Its true form is just a single fox hair.

22:42.070 --> 22:44.180
The fox spirit must be secretly helping her.

22:44.840 --> 22:46.530
Just a single hair has this much power.

22:47.340 --> 22:48.530
If the real Nine-Tailed Fox showed up,

22:48.550 --> 22:49.620
wouldn't it be unstoppable?

22:58.070 --> 22:59.970
Though it was just an illusionary spirit,

23:00.230 --> 23:02.450
you two actually forced it back to its true form.

23:03.230 --> 23:05.900
You both have impressive skills.

23:06.960 --> 23:08.900
How did you do it?

23:09.790 --> 23:12.100
All thanks to His Highness's Luminescent Ring.

23:12.270 --> 23:13.620
Otherwise, we'd have all been done for.

23:14.400 --> 23:15.940
The Luminescent Ring can ward off evil,

23:16.310 --> 23:17.450
but it can't destroy spirits.

23:19.030 --> 23:19.450
Whatever.

23:19.470 --> 23:22.290
Anyway, you faced danger without fear

23:22.310 --> 23:24.340
and didn't abandon your companions.

23:24.680 --> 23:25.820
That deserves praise.

23:26.230 --> 23:28.580
I hope that once you step onto the immortal path,

23:28.920 --> 23:30.010
you'll keep

23:30.310 --> 23:32.420
this pure heart,

23:32.600 --> 23:35.250
support each other, and fight together.

23:38.990 --> 23:40.660
Sir, does that mean

23:41.200 --> 23:42.210
we all passed?

23:50.200 --> 23:53.420
All candidates present have passed the trial.

23:58.340 --> 24:00.290
You're amazing, Xiaobangchui!

24:06.920 --> 24:08.180
Awesome!

24:08.880 --> 24:11.450
- We passed! - Incredible, Xiaobangchui!

24:22.680 --> 24:23.340
Lei Xiuyuan,

24:23.920 --> 24:25.660
I didn't think you'd actually get into the academy.

24:26.310 --> 24:27.450
I underestimated you.

24:28.030 --> 24:28.970
How's Shanhua?

24:29.310 --> 24:31.450
[Mo Chen, Xingzheng Hall]
Not dead yet. But close.

24:32.400 --> 24:34.770
Elder Zhenyun wants you to act quickly.

24:35.100 --> 24:37.140
Otherwise, once she enters the academy,

24:37.270 --> 24:38.820
you might have to go in too.

24:39.270 --> 24:42.100
Shanhua's life hangs by a thread. I'm not in the mood to enter the academy.

24:44.400 --> 24:46.820
That depends on how fast you move.

24:49.100 --> 24:50.100
Isn't there a way to capture

24:51.160 --> 24:52.380
the fox spirit without killing the host?

24:54.310 --> 24:55.660
You've only been together for a few days.

24:56.100 --> 24:57.450
Can't bring yourself to do it already?

24:59.400 --> 25:01.450
The fox spirit is powerful and is protective of its master.

25:02.230 --> 25:02.970
I can't beat it.

25:04.840 --> 25:07.380
Elder Zhenyun anticipated that.

25:19.680 --> 25:20.420
What's this?

25:20.680 --> 25:23.770
Soul-destroying Threads. It can bind the primordial spirit of a monster.

25:24.100 --> 25:26.380
But it'll backfire and destroy your soul meridians.

25:27.550 --> 25:28.100
You...

25:28.710 --> 25:31.290
All masters of the immortal sects cut off worldly ties

25:31.640 --> 25:32.690
and pursue the path of detachment.

25:34.470 --> 25:37.140
Do you think Elder Zhenyun would sacrifice his own cultivation

25:37.400 --> 25:38.380
for an outcast

25:38.960 --> 25:41.180
and let you hinder his path to immortality?

25:44.310 --> 25:44.940
Remember,

25:45.440 --> 25:47.770
Lu Shanhua's life is in your hands.

25:48.270 --> 25:50.100
Send the fox spirit to Xingzheng Hall,

25:50.510 --> 25:52.180
and you'll see him sooner.

25:52.600 --> 25:53.250
Otherwise,

25:54.070 --> 25:56.730
you'll only reunite in the underworld.

26:00.070 --> 26:01.450
So that's how it is.

26:08.470 --> 26:12.490
Xiaobangchui. Xiaobangchui?

26:14.920 --> 26:17.380
Watching the moon? You're lovesick or something?

26:18.750 --> 26:20.380
Little Matchmaker, I was just looking for you.

26:21.440 --> 26:23.100
Who are you looking for this time?

26:23.680 --> 26:25.490
Not looking for someone. I'm keeping tabs on someone.

26:25.990 --> 26:28.770
On whom? That troublemaker?

26:29.790 --> 26:31.250
I think he's got his eye on Riyan.

26:32.790 --> 26:34.140
We definitely need to look into this.

26:34.680 --> 26:37.690
Can't just let that stinky fox end up as a scarf.

26:42.160 --> 26:43.530
Help!

27:09.470 --> 27:12.100
Dual souls entangled, sharing one fate of life and death?

27:14.100 --> 27:14.900
What's going on?

27:15.790 --> 27:17.820
He is after you. I'm out!

27:20.960 --> 27:21.450
Hey,

27:22.030 --> 27:23.140
is that something a friend would do?

27:23.990 --> 27:25.010
Will it ever end?

27:42.550 --> 27:43.180
Your Highness.

27:45.840 --> 27:46.580
Prince Ying,

27:47.600 --> 27:49.530
you keep giving me a hard time.

27:50.070 --> 27:52.420
Are you determined to go against Longming Sanctuary?

27:53.510 --> 27:55.940
Is the Yue State trying to become the next Gaolu State?

27:56.230 --> 27:57.620
You dare threaten me?

27:58.030 --> 28:00.520
I heard that Elder Xuanshan of Xingzheng Hall is struggling

28:00.520 --> 28:01.490
to recover from his old injuries.

28:02.550 --> 28:04.730
If something happens to him,

28:05.600 --> 28:08.450
who will protect Yue?

28:10.030 --> 28:11.940
You slander my country! That's a capital offense!

28:21.070 --> 28:22.100
Xiaobangchui, Luminescent Ring!

28:58.960 --> 29:01.100
Burned... burned to ashes?

29:03.710 --> 29:04.620
First time killing?

29:07.640 --> 29:10.380
Don't be scared. You've removed a threat for the state.

29:10.790 --> 29:11.380
I'll

29:12.790 --> 29:13.940
treat you well from now on.

29:17.160 --> 29:18.290
You just killed people randomly!

29:18.510 --> 29:19.690
Got ground to dust, huh?

29:20.310 --> 29:23.210
That's karma. Justice served!

29:33.440 --> 29:35.100
Are they divine deer from heaven?

29:39.510 --> 29:42.100
They're rainbow deer. You've never seen one?

29:42.550 --> 29:43.940
Making such a fuss.

29:44.550 --> 29:45.490
You've seen one?

29:46.640 --> 29:47.660
Of course.

29:48.070 --> 29:49.250
You definitely haven't.

29:49.600 --> 29:50.660
I had one at home when I was little!

29:50.880 --> 29:51.580
Acting tough.

29:52.600 --> 29:53.450
Tongzhou!

29:56.070 --> 29:57.180
Is one carriage

29:57.550 --> 29:59.290
enough for all of us?

30:00.400 --> 30:01.210
Time to go grab a seat.

30:09.470 --> 30:11.770
Ambergris? Must be rich.

30:18.470 --> 30:19.620
Little brat.

30:21.070 --> 30:22.050
Your Highness, this way.

30:32.550 --> 30:33.340
Have a seat.

30:34.640 --> 30:35.140
Right here.

30:35.400 --> 30:35.820
Okay.

30:46.120 --> 30:47.730
Where did you go after drinking last night?

30:49.070 --> 30:50.690
I was drunk. Slept at the inn.

31:00.270 --> 31:01.050
We're flying!

31:16.200 --> 31:17.760
♪All the way♪

31:18.200 --> 31:20.280
♪From the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

31:20.700 --> 31:23.000
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

31:23.560 --> 31:26.120
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

31:27.000 --> 31:27.960
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

31:27.960 --> 31:28.530
Alright.

31:29.120 --> 31:29.730
What are you doing?

31:30.200 --> 31:30.900
What are you doing?

31:30.900 --> 31:31.840
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

31:31.840 --> 31:33.420
- Just let me see. - Xiaobangchui.

31:33.420 --> 31:35.600
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

31:35.790 --> 31:36.580
Come over here to look.

31:36.580 --> 31:38.840
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

31:39.160 --> 31:39.970
Thanks, Your Highness.

31:39.970 --> 31:42.600
♪The path of light is not far away♪

31:43.230 --> 31:46.340
So many islands. It's beautiful!

31:56.230 --> 31:58.010
This is stunning.

31:59.230 --> 32:00.380
I've never seen anything like it.

32:07.470 --> 32:08.730
Help!

32:10.550 --> 32:11.250
Xiaobangchui!

32:11.600 --> 32:12.250
Xiaobangchui!

32:12.270 --> 32:13.490
What are you doing, Lanya?

32:13.510 --> 32:14.660
Help!

32:22.120 --> 32:22.940
Help!

32:27.920 --> 32:28.530
Hold on tight.

32:52.340 --> 32:54.020
[Mo Yanfan, Chufeng Academy]

33:00.550 --> 33:01.580
I'm a master from the academy.

33:02.600 --> 33:03.860
Are you the freshmen of this year?

33:05.070 --> 33:07.340
Hello, master. I'm Xiaobangchui.

33:07.680 --> 33:10.690
Xiaobangchui? What an interesting name.

33:11.880 --> 33:12.730
And this is...?

33:14.600 --> 33:15.490
I'm Lei Xiuyuan.

33:16.360 --> 33:19.010
Lei Xiuyuan? You're talented.

33:19.960 --> 33:20.860
And you have good character.

33:23.550 --> 33:26.210
The academy is just ahead. Stay steady.

33:40.640 --> 33:41.420
Excuse me.

33:45.970 --> 33:49.200
[Chufeng Academy]

34:28.920 --> 34:29.530
Xiaobangchui!

34:32.700 --> 34:33.300
Are you okay?

34:33.590 --> 34:34.090
I'm fine.

34:40.760 --> 34:41.380
Thanks.

35:00.070 --> 35:00.610
Make way.

35:01.440 --> 35:02.300
- Move aside. - Move aside.

35:04.630 --> 35:05.740
Situ Lanya.

35:07.150 --> 35:08.650
Did you push Xiaobangchui down on purpose?

35:10.590 --> 35:11.900
Yes, I did. So what?

35:13.700 --> 35:15.050
You're going too far!

35:16.070 --> 35:17.130
- Mind your tone! - What did you say?

35:17.150 --> 35:17.900
- Say that again. - You!

35:17.920 --> 35:18.740
- Tongzhou... - What are you doing?

35:23.440 --> 35:25.130
The rules of Chufeng Academy

35:25.670 --> 35:28.650
forbid private fights among disciples.

35:29.220 --> 35:33.530
Anyone who harms a fellow disciple will have their spirit roots destroyed

35:33.700 --> 35:34.610
and be expelled.

35:34.760 --> 35:35.300
But...

35:38.550 --> 35:39.740
There'll be plenty of time.

35:41.550 --> 35:42.380
It's an academy, after all.

35:42.990 --> 35:43.570
Exactly.

35:46.920 --> 35:47.700
Yes, master.

35:53.110 --> 35:54.300
Xiuyuan jumped down after you

35:54.320 --> 35:55.260
without a second thought.

35:56.190 --> 35:57.820
Since when did you two get so close?

35:59.920 --> 36:01.450
He owes me. Guess he's giving himself to me.

36:09.150 --> 36:10.970
Welcome to Chufeng Academy.

36:11.510 --> 36:13.940
The headmaster and masters are waiting at Hongyang Hall.

36:14.700 --> 36:16.820
Follow me.

36:17.670 --> 36:18.090
Let's go.

36:19.670 --> 36:20.130
Let's go.

36:32.280 --> 36:37.380
No learning, no broadening of talent; no will, no success in studies.

36:38.510 --> 36:41.530
Though you were the most outstanding

36:41.550 --> 36:43.490
among the various sects across the lands,

36:44.440 --> 36:47.450
from the moment you step into Chufeng Academy,

36:47.800 --> 36:49.610
you become its disciples.

36:50.030 --> 36:53.130
You must leave mortal affairs behind,

36:53.670 --> 36:55.560
[Zuo Qiu, Chufeng Academy]
focus on your cultivation,

36:55.560 --> 36:56.570
and strive with diligence.

37:01.700 --> 37:03.010
The path of cultivation

37:04.440 --> 37:06.220
requires a dedicated heart.

37:09.920 --> 37:11.260
What is a dedicated heart?

37:11.960 --> 37:14.300
It could be for a personal wish,

37:15.110 --> 37:18.420
or for the greater good. Neither is better or worse.

37:18.990 --> 37:22.840
But you must know good from evil, distinguish right from wrong,

37:22.840 --> 37:23.900
and cultivate your inner mind.

37:25.510 --> 37:28.530
I heard Headmaster Zuo Qiu is a thousand years old.

37:30.320 --> 37:31.940
What elixir of immortality is he on?

37:31.960 --> 37:32.800
[Lin You, Chufeng Academy]

37:35.070 --> 37:38.050
The path of cultivation is long. Remember that always.

37:38.550 --> 37:41.820
Never forget your original intent along the way.

37:44.280 --> 37:45.090
- Yes! - Yes!

37:49.440 --> 37:52.860
Alright, go get settled in.

37:59.070 --> 37:59.970
- Let's go. - Go.

38:01.700 --> 38:02.450
Xiaobangchui.

38:04.960 --> 38:05.820
You stay.

38:13.670 --> 38:14.420
You guys go ahead.

38:28.880 --> 38:29.650
Lei Xiuyuan?

38:34.550 --> 38:35.530
You're waiting for Xiaobangchui?

38:37.400 --> 38:38.090
You're overthinking it.

38:42.110 --> 38:44.970
You said you didn't want to enter the academy.

38:45.990 --> 38:47.420
Why the sudden change of heart?

38:48.800 --> 38:49.570
None of your business.

38:53.220 --> 38:54.420
It's because of that man, isn't it?

38:56.760 --> 38:58.050
His name is Lu Shanhua.

39:10.510 --> 39:11.340
What do you know?

39:16.960 --> 39:18.300
I ran into Senior Mo Chen,

39:18.880 --> 39:19.610
so I know a bit about it.

39:20.360 --> 39:21.530
My uncle Xuanshanzi

39:21.550 --> 39:22.610
is one of the two chief elders

39:22.630 --> 39:23.900
of Xingzheng Hall.

39:24.190 --> 39:24.940
If you need...

39:25.880 --> 39:26.380
I don't need it.

39:26.920 --> 39:27.420
Why?

39:32.550 --> 39:33.820
As a member of the Gaolu imperial family,

39:34.960 --> 39:36.130
haven't you thought about revenge?

39:37.070 --> 39:37.940
Don't you want to restore Gaolu?

39:42.240 --> 39:43.130
Gaolu is long gone.

39:46.960 --> 39:48.130
I won't be a puppet in the conflict

39:48.700 --> 39:49.940
between Yue and Wugou.

39:52.670 --> 39:53.570
Save your schemes.

39:56.840 --> 39:58.090
Xiaobangchui is clever.

39:58.630 --> 40:00.010
She's definitely noticed you scheming

40:00.400 --> 40:01.260
to get close to her.

40:11.670 --> 40:14.340
Sir, have you really never seen my senior brother?

40:16.150 --> 40:17.420
I really haven't.

40:22.190 --> 40:25.220
Your master sent you here,

40:25.840 --> 40:27.970
which means he believed you were destined for this academy.

40:28.280 --> 40:30.530
And the fact that Immortal Dongyang gave you those beads

40:31.550 --> 40:33.170
proves you have an immortal affinity.

40:34.400 --> 40:36.010
Just stay here with peace of mind.

40:36.320 --> 40:37.650
Work hard on your cultivation,

40:38.030 --> 40:39.090
and everything you seek

40:39.800 --> 40:41.420
will fall into place.

40:43.070 --> 40:44.820
When will that be?

40:45.700 --> 40:46.940
I can't even find Senior Brother.

40:47.840 --> 40:49.130
How am I supposed to find Master?

40:57.150 --> 40:57.700
Sir,

40:58.880 --> 41:00.090
are you trying to send me away?

41:01.030 --> 41:02.820
No.

41:03.280 --> 41:05.570
I'd like to give you a formal name.

41:06.150 --> 41:07.010
Would you like that?

41:08.400 --> 41:10.010
Can't "Xiaobangchui" be my formal name?

41:13.840 --> 41:15.050
Your master

41:15.400 --> 41:16.740
just loves cutting corners.

41:18.070 --> 41:21.860
"Xiaobangchui" is really just a nickname.

41:22.440 --> 41:24.050
Since he sent you here,

41:24.280 --> 41:25.610
I might as well be your second master.

41:26.190 --> 41:27.610
So I'll give you a formal name.

41:27.880 --> 41:29.340
Your master would be happy

41:29.670 --> 41:30.820
about it.

41:32.800 --> 41:35.130
That old geezer really did cut corners.

41:38.320 --> 41:39.420
Sir, please give me a new name.

41:42.630 --> 41:44.420
You were raised by your master.

41:44.840 --> 41:46.380
And you're a girl.

41:46.590 --> 41:47.300
Your surname will be Jiang.

41:48.070 --> 41:49.050
As you said,

41:49.190 --> 41:52.450
your master found you

41:52.590 --> 41:54.740
by the river at first light of the day.

41:55.320 --> 41:57.780
That is dawn.

41:58.960 --> 42:01.420
You could be called Jiang Li.
[*"Li" means "dawn"]

42:02.150 --> 42:03.420
Jiang Li?

42:04.440 --> 42:05.610
But "Jiang Li" is a name

42:06.030 --> 42:07.130
that echoes "farewell".
[*A play on homophones]

42:07.880 --> 42:09.650
Since you hope to find your master,

42:09.800 --> 42:11.090
you mustn't leave.

42:15.220 --> 42:16.340
"Fei" means

42:17.280 --> 42:18.380
"not."

42:22.110 --> 42:22.860
Xiaobangchui.

42:23.670 --> 42:24.650
Starting today,

42:25.070 --> 42:25.970
your name is

42:26.360 --> 42:27.970
Jiang Lifei.

42:36.980 --> 42:37.570
Jiang

42:38.300 --> 42:38.970
Li

42:39.990 --> 42:40.610
Fei?

42:42.020 --> 42:43.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.000 --> 42:44.760
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

42:46.480 --> 42:49.380
♪If legends tell of a perilous land♪

42:49.540 --> 42:52.300
♪Why not give it a shot and march with all my might?♪

42:52.420 --> 42:54.940
♪Fearless through a hundred battles, I finally earn my place♪

42:55.100 --> 42:57.140
♪Happy new semester♪

42:57.300 --> 42:59.900
♪Wearing a flowing green robe, like immortal feathers dancing♪

42:59.980 --> 43:02.660
♪The fierce gale is grasped tightly in my palm♪

43:02.900 --> 43:05.340
♪Hearts united, drawing together for a thunderous strike♪

43:05.540 --> 43:07.620
♪Refusing to coast through life♪

43:07.740 --> 43:10.140
♪Though a crisis is sealed before us, I will not give up♪

43:10.260 --> 43:12.980
♪Leaving my silhouette between heaven and earth♪

43:13.420 --> 43:15.940
♪Just as I hesitate and drift away♪

43:16.100 --> 43:17.900
♪A sudden awakening comes♪

43:18.060 --> 43:20.860
♪We will make all the world's pain kneel before us♪

43:20.980 --> 43:23.380
♪The song of victory never stops♪

43:23.540 --> 43:25.700
♪The darkness all turns into illusions♪

43:25.780 --> 43:28.220
♪Unmatched across the Three Realms♪

43:28.300 --> 43:31.260
♪With bare hands, we clench our fists tight♪

43:31.460 --> 43:34.020
♪Soaring high against the wind to hunt the enemy♪

43:34.180 --> 43:38.620
♪Together we shatter the filth and malice of this world♪

43:38.740 --> 43:41.700
♪Guarding our ground, we rise to the peak♪

43:41.940 --> 43:44.340
♪No need to wait around for natural gifts♪

43:44.500 --> 43:47.260
♪Learning knows no end; we unite as one♪

43:47.260 --> 43:49.980
♪The howling wind obeys my command♪

